#: ../../changelog.rst:398
msgid "Added the \"Advanced/Simple\" editors to the :command:`fluxbox` keys page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:401
msgid ""
"The process of finding icons has been reworked for better functionality."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:404
msgid "New wallpaper sizing options: \"Fit\" and \"Full\"."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:406
msgid ""
"Released a new desktop plugin: \"rssreader\". This plugin displays an active"
" RSS feed in a configurable window set to the lower right corner of the "
"screen by default. This plugin supports the RSS v0.91 and v2.0 standards."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:411
msgid ""
"Reset which directories are monitored for apps to be installed into every "
"time the watcher updates (this fixes the detection of KDE apps being "
"installed/removed)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:415
msgid ""
"Improved backend search routine for finding .desktop files or binaries."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:417
msgid ""
"The calendar plugin will now move to next day if the system remains on over "
"24 hours."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:420
msgid ""
":command:`lumina-fm` will remove broken symlinks when deleting directories."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:423
msgid "Load previous screen config on Lumina start."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:425
msgid ""
"Fixed the detection and usage of the \"mailto:\" option in :command:`lumina-"
"open`. This also changes the default mimetype used for email applications to"
" \"application/email\"."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:429
msgid "The start menu now hides duplicate \"favorite\" entries."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:431
msgid ""
"Added a search bar to the start menu to provide users an efficient method to"
" search for apps or utilities directly."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:434
msgid ""
"User button - now displays only one entry for applications linked via both "
"the desktop and favorites category."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:437
msgid ""
"The nongrouping task manager now uses a uniform size for panel buttons."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:439
msgid ""
"Pressing the :kbd:`Windows button` will open the Start Menu/User Button/ "
"Application Menu, whichever is the default system button."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:442
msgid "Build systems updates:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:444
msgid ""
"Localizations have been moved from `NO_I18N` to `WITH_I18N`. This will "
"ensure that the source version of the localizations are not installed unless"
" explicitly requested (since the \"real\" localization files are in the "
"lumina-i18n repo - these source files are the autogenerated ones before "
"getting sent up to the pootle localization system)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:450
msgid ""
"Users can add custom :file:`luminaDesktop.conf` files for a particular "
"operating system to simplify builds. Customized :file:`luminaDesktop.conf` "
"files can also pull in default wallpapers for the system."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:454
msgid ""
"To bypass OS settings check - use \"DEFAULT_SETTINGS=<some OS>\" in "
":file:`luminaDesktop.conf`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:457
msgid "A new theme titled \"Glass\" has been added."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:459
msgid ""
"Added :kbd:`Control+[shift]+Tab` shortcuts for cycling between open windows "
"in grouped order rather than open order (:kbd:`alt+[shift]+tab` will do open"
" order)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:463
msgid ""
"Non-applauncher desktop plugins now fill in from the bottom-right of the "
"screen. This provides easily visible separation between the auto-generated "
"launchers and other plugins."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:467
msgid ""
"Have the :command:`lumina-open` dialog show applications on the main list "
"which also have the hidden flag set (since this is for using the app to "
"launch something else - these apps are now valid to show)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:471
msgid ""
"Lumina Text Edit has a new symlink :command:`lte` for quick launching the "
"editor from the command line."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:474
msgid ""
"Fixed the symlink creation routine in :command:`lumina-textedit` to work "
"with package systems."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:477
msgid ""
"Setup a recursive :command:`xinit` call within the :command:`start-lumina-"
"desktop` binary as needed. This call detects if an \"X\" session is already "
"active, and will startup \"X\" if inactive."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:481
msgid ""
"Added the ability for custom, system-wide environment variable settings "
"within :file:`/usr/local/etc/lumina-environment.conf` This allows a system "
"admin the ability to setup customized build environment settings on a global"
" basis. User settings are treated as overrides for the system settings."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:487
msgid "Disabled autoraise in :command:`fluxbox` by default."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:489
msgid ""
"Fixed a crash when right-clicking a non-applauncher desktop plugin and "
"removing it."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:492
msgid ""
"Fixed a crash within the userbutton plugin which would happen after clearing"
" out one of the scroll areas."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:495
msgid ""
"Fixed the resizeMenu's mouse event handling to ensure it keeps control of "
"the mouse during resize events."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:498
msgid ""
"Add a new :file:`LuminaUtils` function for converting a .desktop or binary "
"name into a full path (searching all the various system directories until it"
" finds the file)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:502
msgid ""
"The quick command run routine will now never hang the system for more than 1"
" second of inactivity from the subprocess."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:505
msgid ""
"Allow the \"save file as\" option within lumina-textedit to always be "
"available and not dependent on changes to the file."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:512
msgid "Lumina 0.9.0"
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:514
msgid ""
"Created a \"Common Applications\" tab in the :menuselection:`Lumina "
"Configuration Utility --> \"Applications\"` section and moved common "
"applications settings from the \"File Defaults\" tab."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:518
msgid ""
"Changed the default wallpapers for Lumina/PC-BSD and added some more 4K "
"Lumina wallpapers."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:521
msgid ""
"Updated :command:`lumina-screenshot`: Added a new quicksave option and "
"launch editor button for opening a full editor, windows to be snapshot may "
"now be clicked on for selection rather than using the list of open windows, "
"and screenshots may be cropped as needed within the utility before saving "
"them to a file."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:527
msgid ""
"Added new Utility: :command:`lumina-textedit`. This is a simple plaintext "
"editor with syntax highlighting, find/replace support, line numbers, and "
"bracket highlighting."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:531
msgid ""
"Updated the Lumina theme engine to no longer use stylesheets to modify non-"
"desktop applications (including the Lumina tools/utilities). This opens the "
"door for a full Qt5 theme plugin to be used for non-desktop utilities "
"instead."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:536
msgid ""
"Updated which XDG mime-types are used for the default web browser and file "
"manager. This should make it align a bit better with what applications "
"expect (if they try to read/use the database directly - such as some popular"
" web browsers do)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:541
msgid "Updated Linux harddrive device detection (\"nvme\" devices)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:543
msgid "Added Gentoo Linux support and an \"ebuild\" file."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:545
msgid "Cleanup of some minor source syntax issues with Qt 5.6"
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:547
msgid ""
"Fixed a number of multi-monitor issues. Screen resizes/changes will now be "
"properly detected on the fly (on any system - including VM's), and panels "
"will be placed properly on monitors not aligned with the y=0 axis."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:552
msgid ""
"Ensured the current system volume gets saved on logout so it can be reloaded"
" on next login (in case the volume was changed by some external tool during "
"the session)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:556
msgid ""
"Added new startup binary: :command:`start-lumina-desktop`. This will be used"
" as the primary \"entry point\" for launching the desktop as opposed to the "
"\"Lumina-DE\" binary (please adjust your .xinitrc files and wrapper scripts "
"as needed). The xsession desktop entry that Lumina installs was already "
"changed to run this tool, so graphical desktop managers should be unaffected"
" by this change. This tool will eventually be used to perform the X session "
"setup/configuration (so CLI users will not need to run :command:`xinit` or "
":command:`startx` directly anymore), but the X integration has not been "
"implemented yet."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:566
msgid ""
"Updated the FreeBSD appstore shortcut to point to the new appcafe.desktop "
"file from PC-BSD."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:569
msgid ""
"Cleaned many old shell scripts from the source tree (not needed for builds "
"any more)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:572
msgid "Streamlined the build procedures slightly."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:574
msgid ""
"Reorganized the source tree. Now all the Lumina tools/utilities are kept "
"separate from the general build scripts/files within a :file:`src-qt5` "
"directory, and additionally organized into categories (core, core-utils, "
"desktop-utils). Automated build systems should not be impacted by this "
"change, as the main project file (lumina.pro) has been left in the same "
"place within the repository and just had all the internal paths adjusted "
"accordingly."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:583
msgid ""
"Updated all the installed desktop entries to use relative paths for the "
"icons (better cross-OS support)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:586
msgid "Fixed the detection of \"sloppy\" URL's given to lumina-open."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:588
msgid ""
"Adjusted one of the include files for the Lumina library so external "
"applications can now link against the lib without the availability of the "
"Lumina source tree (although still not recommended)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:592
msgid ""
"Stability fix for the desktop when an invalid desktop plugin is "
"set/registered."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:599
msgid "Lumina 0.8.8"
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:601
msgid ""
"Add 3 different view modes for applications in the start menu: Alphabetical "
"(no categories), Partial Categories, or Categories (need to click the "
"category to go into it and see the applications)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:605
msgid ""
"Make the symlink icon overlays a bit smaller at 1/3 icon size instead of "
"1/2."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:608
msgid ""
"Add a new button for the audio controls to the left side of the "
":menuselection:`Start --> Preferences` menu for muting and unmuting audio."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:612
msgid ""
"The RPM spec for Fedora/CentOS has been refactored.  Within the limits of "
"supporting both Fedora and CentOS 7, 32-bit and 64-bit builds can be done "
"from the same spec, so that it complies with Fedora's guidelines on how a "
"package should be structured."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:617
msgid "Improvements to the notepad desktop plugin."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:619
msgid ""
"Redo the \"App Menu\" panel plugin so that it uses a self-contained menu and"
" lists the logout options at the bottom."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:622
msgid ""
"Fix sorting of \"favorites\" items in the \"Start\" menu to be sorted by "
"display name instead of file name."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:625
msgid ""
"Add new options for loading new wallpaper files in :command:`lumina-config`:"
" Single Directory (all images within the directory) and Recursive Directory "
"(all images in the selected directory and all sub-directories)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:630
msgid ""
"Add support for selecting a ZFS snapshot by name, in addition to the current"
" time-slider."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:633
msgid "NetBSD is now a supported build target."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:635
msgid ""
"Add the ability to change monitor resolutions in :command:`lumina-xconfig`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:638
msgid "Add support for the Intel backlight, if available, on FreeBSD systems."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:640
msgid "Fixed a translation bug for the Portuguese language."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:642
msgid "Fix a crash on FreeBSD 11.x when removing a desktop icon."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:644
msgid ""
"Fix a multi-threading issue randomly causing :command:`lumina-fm` to crash "
"when opening a directory."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:647
msgid ""
"Fix some resize bugs with the custom resizeMenu class which is used by the "
"\"Start\" menu."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:650
msgid ""
"Multiple fixes for resolution detection as well as graphical glitches that "
"were causing menus to behave unpredictably."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:657
msgid "Lumina 0.8.7"
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:659
msgid "Convert everything to XCB and remove XLib dependencies."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:661
msgid "Update DragonFlyBSD support."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:663
msgid ""
"Adjust build procedures to better support multiple concurrent threads using "
"the \"-j<#threads>\" :command:`make` option."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:666
msgid ""
"Add better relative path support for launching applications in the mimetype "
"database."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:669
msgid ""
"Add support for a new instance of a LuminaSingleInstance application using "
"the \"-new-instance\" CLI flag."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:672
msgid ""
"Add better fallback methodology for detecting and fixing stale single-"
"instance flags."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:675
msgid ""
"Now uses the Qt5-Concurrent build module for additional multi-threading "
"support in various utilities."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:678
msgid ""
"Add support for selecting a mouse cursor theme (requires session restart)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:681
msgid ""
"Add new color schemes: Grey-Dark, Solarized-Light, Solarized-Dark, and Blue-"
"Light."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:684
msgid "Customize the Lumina-default theme."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:686
msgid ""
"Add inheritance to theme files and convert the Lumina-default to inherit the"
" \"None\" theme."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:693
msgid ""
"Add support for various background image scaling and placement options."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:696
msgid ""
"Add a number of new desktop shortcuts for the session. This requires "
"existing users to remove their :file:`~/.lumina/fluxbox-keys` before logging"
" in to get the new settings."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:700
msgid ""
"Clean up the panel activation and detection routines to better respond to "
"mouse-over events, particularly for auto-hidden panels."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:703
msgid ""
"Completely overhaul the desktop plugin container system. Now it is "
"completely drag and drop based with an intelligent grid of items and "
"locations. Right-click, or click and hold, an item to open a menu of "
"additional plugin configuration options. Note that any previous plugin "
"locations will be reset to their defaults during the update to this new "
"system."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:710
msgid ""
"Add support for dropping files and directories from other applications onto "
"the desktop, creating a symlink to the desktop folder when appropriate."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:714
msgid ""
"Add font outlining to all desktop items so that the text is visible even if "
"the font color blends into the background image."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:717
msgid ""
"ZFS snapshot browsing is now seemlessly embedded within the directory viewer"
" of :ref:`Insight File Manager`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:720
msgid ""
"Add support for either tabs or columns when viewing multiple directories at "
"once."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:723
msgid ""
"Replace the \"Icon View\" mode with the ability to adjust the icon sizes as "
"desired."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:726
msgid ""
"Add support for running the slideshow viewer and multimedia player in the "
"background as separate tabs. Add the ability to zoom in/out on a slideshow "
"image as desired."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:730
msgid ""
"Add full drag and drop implementation to Insight File Manager. Can drag "
"files and directories to external applications that support the standard "
"\"text/urilist\" Mimetype for drag and drop operations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:734
msgid ""
"Directory and thumbnail loading is now a couple orders of magnitude faster "
"than before. The thumbnail loading routine is now a completely separate "
"background thread, preventing any delays in application functionality while "
"loading."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:739
msgid "Add support for the \"back\" mouse button when viewing a directory."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:745
msgid ""
"Add support for detecting and allowing user-local Fluxbox themes in addition"
" to system-local themes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:752
msgid ""
"Update the :ref:`Interface` used for panel configuration so that it is much "
"easier to read and use."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:759
msgid ""
"Overhaul the \"Clock\" panel plugin. Now it provides a menu with a calendar "
"as well as an option for the user to instantly switch the time zone."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:763
msgid ""
"New \"Start Menu\" panel plugin is a Windows-esque system menu which "
"incorporates the functionality of both the user button and the system "
"dashboard in one place. This plugin also supports creating and removing "
"desktop links for applications, as well as \"quick-launch\" buttons for "
"adding applications to the panel."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:769
msgid ""
"Update the \"Workspace Switcher\" panel plugin so it stays in sync with "
"external changes to the current workspace."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:772
msgid ""
"New \"Line\" panel plugin provides a simple visual line to provide "
"separation between plugins."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:775
msgid "Fix or bypass some Fluxbox window placement bugs."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:777
msgid ""
"Fix some bugs in the user button regarding file and directory removals."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:780
msgid ""
"Clean up a number of built-in text strings for clarity and consistency."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:783
msgid ""
"Ensure that graphical sliders for adjusting screen brightness only go down "
"to 10% to prevent the user from blacking out their screen entirely."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:787
msgid ""
"Update the support for non-xterm terminal emulators to be opened within a "
"particular directory."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:792
msgid ""
"Update support for sticky windows to appear in the task manager on all "
"workspaces."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:795
msgid ""
"Clean up a number of possible bugs with regards to how external application "
"might be launched or used. This fixes the random race condition where a "
"process finished but the thread in Lumina which called it still thinks it is"
" running."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:800
msgid ""
"Ensure that all calendar widgets on the desktop or panel update as necessary"
" to ensure the correct date is shown during multiple-day sessions."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:807
