#: ../../changelog.rst:24
msgid "**Major Changes**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:26
msgid ""
"Dismantle the Lumina library (:file:`libLuminaUtils.so`). This is no longer "
"needed or installed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:28
msgid ""
"Disable the internal Lumina Theme engine from all utilities. Now it is used "
"only by the desktop while all applications use the global Qt5 theme engine."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:31
msgid "New Panel Plugins:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:33
msgid ""
"*audioplayer* (panel version of the desktop plugin with the same name): "
"Allows the user to load and play audio files directly through the desktop "
"itself."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:36
msgid ""
"*jsonmenu* (panel version of the menu plugin with the same name): Allows use"
" of an external utility or script to generate a menu or contents on demand."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:40
msgid ""
"New Menu Plugin *lockdesktop*: Menu option for instantly locking the desktop"
" session."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:43
msgid ""
"New :command:`lumina-archiver` utility: A pure Qt5 front-end to the *tar* "
"utility for managing and creating archives. *Archiver* can also use the *dd*"
" utility to burn an :file:`*.img` file to a USB device for booting."
msgstr ""

